videos.description: Tennessee's Jordan Bone lobs the baseline out-of-bounds pass to Grant Williams, who climbs the ladder and smashes home the and-1 alley-oop.
videos.headline: Williams fouled as he stuffs alley-oop inbound pass

videos.description: Grant Williams displays a series of jabs, gets his defender to bite on a pump fake, then drop steps for a ferocious right-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Williams skies for monstrous right-handed slam

videos.description: Grant Williams says Tennessee's toughness gives them the ability to fight through adversity, as the Volunteers defeat Louisiana 87-65.
videos.headline: Williams says Tennessee instills toughness to game
